#Control Type	    Description	Prefix to Use	Common Signal
# Push Button	    Standard button	pushButton	clicked
# Radio Button  	Radio toggle button	radio	clicked
# Checkbox      	Checkbox toggle	checkbox	stateChanged
# Combobox      	Dropdown list	combo	currentIndexChanged
# List Widget   	Selectable list control that can contain many items	list	currentRowChanged
# Frame	Container    object that can contain other controls.	frame	
# Line Edit	Text box, used for allowing user input	lineEdit	
# Label	Non-editable text display	label	
# Menu Action	Choice in a program menu	        action	triggered

